H0.text: Blood cells are the cells that the skeletal system makes.

H1.text: Osteoclast is a cell that the skeletal system makes.

H2.text: Dendritic cells are made by the skeletal system.

H3.text: Brain cells are cells that the skeletal system makes.

A4.text: Osteoclasts are derived from the hematopoietic lineage, osteoblasts are derived from mesenchymal stem cells.
